SHUTDOWN
  Gracefully shut down the game server.  (Deity only.)

SYNTAX
  shutdown [<delay-seconds>]
  shut     [<delay-seconds>]

DESCRIPTION
  Initiates a server shutdown.  Only the deity (country 0) can
  use this command.

  [delay-seconds]  - seconds to wait before shutting down.
                     Default is 0 (immediate).

  All connected players are notified and disconnected before the
  server exits.  The database is flushed to disk safely.

EXAMPLE
  shutdown                  immediate shutdown
  shutdown 60               shutdown in 60 seconds

SEE ALSO
  enable  disable  add
